ach. Moreover, we validate and compare the outcomes\nfor predicted pore pressure with mud-weight data from a blind well. The fast\nproxy of analyzing the depth-positioning of seismic horizons proposed in this\nwork yields similar uncertainty quantification results in pore pressure\nprediction compared to the benchmark. These fast proxies make the BGBM\nmethodology efficient and practical.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 19:34:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-21"}
