ot only biomolecular structures, but whole structure\nensembles and, ultimately, 'molecular movies'.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 20:59:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Apr 2023 13:42:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-17"}
