f the properties of r-process nuclei, such as with the Facility\nfor Rare Isotope Beams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Feb 2023 23:41:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 17:24:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-24"}
